---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="AI Development – Onyx Labs"
  description="End-to-end AI development, from prototypes to production-grade systems."
>
  <section class="content-main">
    <div class="container shell">
      <div class="content-layout">
        <div>
          <h1 class="content-heading">From proof-of-concept to hardened AI systems.</h1>
          <p class="content-lede">
            Onyx Labs designs and builds end-to-end AI systems — from prototypes that prove value
            to production platforms that scale.
          </p>
          <div class="content-tags">
            <span class="tag">LLM Applications</span>
            <span class="tag">Retrieval & Tooling</span>
            <span class="tag">Evaluations & Guardrails</span>
            <span class="tag">MLOps & Observability</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="content-panel">
          <h3>We typically own</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Solution and data architecture.</li>
            <li>Model selection and integration.</li>
            <li>Evaluation and safety harnesses.</li>
            <li>Deployment, monitoring, and handover.</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="content-panel">
          <h3>LLM-powered products</h3>
          <p>
            We build AI-native features such as copilots, agents, and assistants that integrate
            with your existing products and workflows.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Task-specific assistants and copilots.</li>
            <li>Retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) systems.</li>
            <li>Workflow automation and orchestration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="content-panel">
          <h3>Infrastructure & reliability</h3>
          <p>
            Our work includes the less glamorous pieces: logging, evaluation, and operations that
            keep AI systems reliable once they ship.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Evaluation pipelines and test harnesses.</li>
            <li>Production monitoring and alerting.</li>
            <li>Cost, latency, and reliability tuning.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-section">
        <div class="section-header flex justify-between align-items-start flex-wrap gap-3 mb-3">
          <div>
            <div class="section-title">Engagement models</div>
            <p class="section-subtitle mb-0">
              We can own full delivery or embed alongside your in-house teams.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <div class="card-onyx">
            <div class="card-label">Build</div>
            <div class="card-title">End-to-end delivery</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              A cross-functional team that designs, builds, and ships a scoped AI system on a
              defined timeline.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-onyx">
            <div class="card-label">Partner</div>
            <div class="card-title">Embedded engineering</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              Onyx Labs engineers work side-by-side with your team to accelerate a critical AI
              initiative.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-onyx">
            <div class="card-label">Platform</div>
            <div class="card-title">AI platform foundations</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              We help you stand up the core components required to support multiple AI products.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
